quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  10,53,"Bayakucela (Muhammad) ukuba ubaxelele ukuba: “Ingaba iyinyani na (into yokuba isohlwayo neMini yokuGqibela siza kwenzeka)?” Yithi: “Ewe! Ndifunga ngeNkosi yam! Iyinyani ngokwenene yaye anisayi kuphuncula kuzo!”"
  10,54,"Yaye ukuba umntu ngamnye owenze ububi ebengaba nabo bonke ubutyebi beli hlabathi aze afune ukuzisindisa kuAllâh ngokuzihlawulela ngabo (bebungazi kwamkelwa kuye) baya kuba lusizi ezintliziyweni zabo xa besibona isohlwayo, yaye baza kugwetywa ngobulungisa akukho bugwenxa buya kwenziwa kubo"
  10,55,"Ngokungathandabuzekiyo, inene, konke okusemazulwini nasemhlabeni kokuka-Allâh. Akuthandabuzeki, inene, isithembiso sika-Allâh siyinyaniso kodwa uninzi lwabo alwazi"
  10,56,"NguYe Onika ubomi, Enze ukufa, yaye (nonke) niza kubuyela kuYe"
  10,57,Hini na bantu! Icebiso elilungileyo elivela eNkosini yenu lifikile kuni (i’Kur`ân) liyalela (ukwenziwa) kwako konke okulungileyo lisalela ukwenziwa kwako konke okungendawo likwanyanga oko kusezintliziyweni zenu liyinkumbuzo nenceba kumakholwa
  10,58,"Yithi: “KubuBele buka-Allâh, nakuBabalo lwaKhe (abantu) mabagcobe.” Oko kokona kulungileyo (endaweni yobutyebi) abanabo"
  10,59,"Yithi: “Khanindixeleleni, kungani na ukuba imbonelelo uAllâh Ayithumele kuni niyenza ivumeleke okanye ibe yinqambi nje!” Yithi: “NguAllâh kusini na Onivumele (ukuba nenze loo nto), okanye niziqambela ubuxoki ngoAllâh kusini na?”"
  10,60,"Yintoni kanye ecingwa ngabo baqamba ubuxoki ngoAllâh, ngeMini yoVuko, Inene, uAllâh UnobuBele ebantwini, kodwa uninzi lwabo alunambulelo"
  10,61,"Akukho bani, nawe na (Muhammad) owenza nasiphi na isenzo esilungileyo okanye ucengceleze nasiphi na isahluko se’Kur`ân okanye nina (bantu) benza nokuba sesiphi na isenzo Size Thina Singabi ngomaNgqina aso xa nisenza. Kwaye akukho nto ifihlakeleyo eNkosini yakho nokuba ilisuntswana na emhlabeni okanye ezulwini, akukho nto incinane kunoko nenkulu kunoko (engabhalwanga eNcwadini ecacileyo)"
  10,62,"Yabonani! Inene, kwii-Awliyâ7 zika-Allâh akuyi kubakho koyika kuzo kungayi kubakho kuxhalaba"
  10,63,Abo bakholwayo babedla ngokoyika uAllâh kakhulu
  10,64,"Okwabo zindaba ezivuyisayo kubomi beli hlabathi, nakuBomi oBuzayo. Akuyi kubakho kuguquka eMazwini ka-Allâh. Le iya kuba yimpumelelo enkulu"
  10,65,"Kananjalo musa ukuvumela iintetho zabo zikukhubekise wena (Muhammad) kuba onke amandla nentlonipheko zezika-Allâh. Yena nguSokuva, uSolwazi"
  10,66,"Ewe nje! Inene kokuka-Allâh konke okusemazulwini nasemhlabeni, naye nabani na osemhlabeni. Ke bona abo banqula, babize kubambi ngaphandle koAllâh, enyanisweni abalandeli mahlulelane (abathi ngaka-Allâh), koko balandela uqash-qash yaye baqamba ubuxoki"
  10,67,"NguYe Owanikhethela ubusuku ukuba niphumle ngabo, nemini ukuba nenze izinto ezibonakalayo ngayo. Inene koku kukho imiqondiso kubantu abaphulaphulayo"
  10,68,"Bathi: “UAllâh Uzele unyana.” Makazukiswe Yena, Yena UsisiTyebi, okwaKhe kuko konke okusemazulwini nako konke okusemhlabeni. Akukho gunya ninalo mayela noku. Kanti nithetha eningakwaziyo na ngoAllâh"
  10,69,"Yithi: “Inene, abo baqamba ubuxoki ngoAllâh asokuze babe nempumelelo.”"
  10,70,"Lulonwabo lwexeshana olwalo mhlaba! Ukanti kuThi kulapho baza kubuyela khona, Size Sibenze bangcamle isohlwayo sesingcungcuthekiso esibuhlungu kuba baye bala ukukholwa (kuAllâh)"